Sorry. <br>
This thread is discussing the benefits of haste vs no haste.  It has been established that haste is greater than no haste due to the huge benefits you gain from a single item. <br>
<br>
So my points are:<br>
Have fun.<br>
Use what you want.<br>
Play with who you want and how you want.<br>
Hasted you will be able to kill more mobs, kill mobs faster, die less and be significantly more effective over an all-things-the-same-but-haste paladin.<br>
<br>
Who you are, or who you know, or how much fun you like to have or what wig you like to wear when playing the game has no bearing whatsoever on this discussion. The point is haste vs no haste and the generally agreed upon best solution is to be hasted. No one ac item can increase your effectiveness like a haste item can. Period. <br>
<br>
This is a forum for discussing equipment upgrades and their benefits. I realize that the numbers are boring to some, but they are necessary to prove the point. There is a roleplaying forum where you can post interesting stories and ask about lore and what not. In a discussion on the benefits of haste you need the numbers because subjective experiences are just that. Subjective. To whatever your perception of the event was as opposed to the actual event. <br>
